name: BuckeyeFootballCalendar
0:
”Alexa, ask Buckeye Football Calendar what game is today”
”Ask Buckeye Football Calendar who does Ohio State play on October 28th”
”Ask Buckeye Football Calendar who do the Buckeyes play Saturday”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: buckeye football calendar
Developer Terms of Use
des: Want to know if there's an Ohio State game on Saturday? Just ask the Buckeye Football Calendar. This continuously updated calendar will let you know who the Buckeyes are playing and, if available, what time.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
